# üñäÔ∏è Visual Studio Code Installation Guide

## üì• Download

Visit [https://code.visualstudio.com](https://code.visualstudio.com) and download the appropriate version:
- **Windows**: `.exe` installer
- **macOS**: `.zip` installer for Intel chip

## ‚öôÔ∏è Install Steps

### Windows
1. Run `.exe` installer
2. Click ‚ÄúNext‚Äù through wizard
3. Use default settings
4. Finish and launch from Start Menu or desktop



## ‚úÖ Verification
- Open VS Code ‚Üí Should load Welcome screen
- Optional: Open Terminal and use `code` command (if added to PATH)

## üí° Troubleshooting
- If `code` isn‚Äôt recognized, open VS Code ‚Üí Command Palette ‚Üí `Shell Command: Install 'code' command`
